Title: Einhell 4465095 TC-MG 220/1 E Multi-Tool 220W 240V EINTCMG220
Description:
The Einhell TC-MG 220/1 E Multi-Tool is a compact and highly versatile machine that can perform a variety of tasks: sawing, sanding, scraping and much more are quick and easy to perform with this handy all-rounder. The electronic speed control ensures that the power is exactly tailored to your operation. It has a robust aluminium driveshaft that has been designed for intensive use. The soft painted housing mount and mounted soft grip make it comfortable and easy to grip.

Supplied with:

1 x Delta Sanding Disc With Dust Extraction.
1 x Sanding Paper.
1 x Scraper.
1 x RAID-Blade For Wood.
1 x Dust Extraction Adapter.
2 x Allen Keys.

Specifications:

Input Power: 220W.
No Load Speed: 15,000-22,000/min.
Oscillation Angle: 3°.
Grinding Area: 90 x 90 x 90mm.
Weight: 1.8kg.
